  "prompt": "How can I tell if a guy likes me or is just using me?",
  "response": "Here are some signs to help you distinguish:\n\nSigns he genuinely likes you:\n- He shows consistent interest in your life\n- Introduces you to friends/family\n- Makes time for you\n- Communicates openly and honestly\n- Respects your boundaries\n- Wants to build an emotional connection\n\nSigns he may be using you:\n- Only contacts you when he wants something\n- Avoids commitment or serious conversations\n- Doesn't invest time or effort in the relationship\n- Primarily focuses on physical intimacy\n- Doesn't share personal details about himself\n- Disappears or becomes distant after getting what he wants\n\nTrust your instincts and watch for red flags. If something feels off, it probably is. Good communication and setting clear boundaries are key.\n\nWould you like to discuss specific situations or behaviors you've noticed?",
